Classes in CFG used by CFG
BasicBlock
          This class contains a block number and all the instructions belong to that basic block.
Defs_Uses
          This class represents a definition or a use in a basic block and contains which basic block it belongs it, which line number it represents, and which variable it is.
Edge
          This class represents an edge in the CFG, flows from U to V.
Function
          This class represents an individual function.
Instruction
          This class represents each instruction line in the bytecode.
Line
          Represents a line of code in the original php file and contains the corresponding bytecode.
